I tidak dapat ditemukan.','The request size is too large.'=>'Ukuran permintaan terlalu besar.','The request is too long.'=>'Permintaan terlalu panjang.','Too many requests. Please try again later.'=>'Terlalu banyak permintaan. Silakan coba lagi nanti.','Your translation quota has been reached.'=>'Kuota terjemahan Anda telah tercapai.','We could not process your request. Please try again later.'=>'Kami tidak dapat memproses permintaan Anda. Silakan coba lagi nanti.','There is an error on the DeepL service and your request could not be processed.'=>'Terjadi kesalahan pada layanan DeepL dan permintaan Anda tidak dapat diproses.','DeepL API Type'=>'Jenis API DeepL','Pro'=>'Pro','Free'=>'Gratis','Select the type of DeepL API you want to use.'=>'Pilih jenis API DeepL yang ingin Anda gunakan.','DeepL API Key'=>'Kunci API DeepL','Visit <a href="%s" target="_blank">this link</a> to see how you can set up an API key and control API costs.'=>'Kunjungi <a href="%s" target="_blank">tautan ini</a> untuk melihat cara menyiapkan kunci API dan mengontrol biaya API.','Translator'=>'Penerjemah',' TranslatePress Settings'=>' Pengaturan TranslatePress','Allow this user to translate the website.'=>'Izinkan pengguna ini untuk menerjemahkan situs web.','(inactive)'=>'(tidak aktif)','Taxonomy Slugs'=>'Slug Taksonomi','Search Taxonomy Slugs'=>'Cari Slug Taksonomi','Taxonomy Slug'=>'Slug Taksonomi','Term Slugs'=>'Slug Istilah','Search Term Slugs'=>'Cari Slug Istilah','Term Slug'=>'Slug Istilah','Taxonomy'=>'Taksonomi','Filter by Taxonomy'=>'Filter menurut taksonomi','Post Slugs'=>'Slug Pos','Search Post Slugs'=>'Cari Slug Pos','Post ID'=>'ID Pos','Post Type'=>'Jenis Pos','Filter by Post Type'=>'Filter berdasarkan Jenis Pos','Published'=>'Diterbitkan','Any Post Status'=>'Status Pos Apa Saja','Post Type Base Slugs'=>'Slug Dasar Tipe Pos','Post Type Base Slug'=>'Slug Dasar Tipe Pos','Search Post Type Base Slugs'=>'Cari Slug Dasar Tipe Pos','WooCommerce Slugs'=>'Slug WooCommerce','WooCommerce Slu